## Overview

This challenge is basically about building a news homepage that relate news about technology. The project is built majorly with HTML and Css with a little Javascript which is essential in mobile version.

### The challenge

Users should be able to:

- View the optimal layout for the interface depending on their device's screen size
- See hover and focus states for all interactive elements on the page

